5. what is the command to see the users

    tail -5 /etc/passwd

6. Create groups 1.dev 2.qa 3.prod 4.staging
   
[root@BlueFox ~]# groupadd dev
[root@BlueFox ~]# groupadd qa
[root@BlueFox ~]# groupadd prod
[root@BlueFox ~]# groupadd staging


7. what is the command to see the groups
    tail -5 /etc/group

